#: ../../image_editor/color_management.rst:97
msgid ""
"To back up a little bit and look at the first color profile an image "
"encounters, that is, the camera profile (see (1) immediately above) - Libraw "
"can in fact apply your camera profile for you (Libraw uses lcms internally). "
